  "title": "Warehouse Assistant/ Storekeeper #80443",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Wholesale of Food Service Product</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Warehouse Assistant/ Store Assistant</strong></li><li>Working Location: Penjuru Lane</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days (Monday-Friday, starts from 7.30am/ 8.00am/ 8.30am (9 hours); Saturday half day)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + OT Pay+ PB</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Perform timely and accurate checking and packing of orders.</li><li>Pick stock in a timely and accurate manner.</li><li>Sort packed orders by delivery route after packing.</li><li>Sort incoming stock from the warehouse.</li><li>Meet the KPIs set and comply with all safety requirements.</li><li>Participate in the annual warehouse stock count and warehouse sales.</li><li>Perform ad-hoc duties as assigned.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Able to handle heavy loads up to 20kg.</li><li>Able to communicate effectively with team members.</li><li>Possess a valid Forklift license.</li><li>Willing to work at height, with WSQ Working at Height training provided</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#80443 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
